name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Ala IBRAHIM, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 8th day of April, 2010, the Petition for Reinstatement of Right to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel is direct to file the Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 7 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Ala IBRAHIM, Petitioner.

April 8, 2010.
